'''Bruce French''' ([[July 4]], [[1940s#1945|1945]] &ndash; [[February 7]], [[2025]])<ref name="Hollywood">{{WebCite|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/tv/tv-news/bruce-french-dead-passions-1236131400|title=Bruce French, ‘Passions’ Actor and a Veteran of the Stage, Dies at 79|author=Mike Barnes|date=2025-02-08|work=[[Wikipedia:The Hollywood Reporter|''The Hollywood Reporter'']]|archivedate=20260114082955}}</ref> was a voice actor in the [[Star Wars (radio)|''Star Wars'' radio drama]]. His role was unidentified.

French passed away on February 7, 2025 due to complications from Alzheimer's.<ref name="Hollywood" /> 

